    <stitle>International&#174; T 444E Diesel Engine - Model Years Late 1997 to 2003 - Manifolds - Installation</stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcsubsec>
        <title>Installation</title>
        <svcsubsecinfo>
            <specpara>
                <note>
                    <para>When installing exhaust manifolds, only use prevailing torque flanged-head bolts with
                        interference thread.
                    </para>
                </note>
            </specpara>
        </svcsubsecinfo>
        <svcproc svcproctype="torque" graphiccount="3">
            <title>Right Exhaust Manifold</title>
            <figure id="f1200309" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic filename="../figeg3/EG3311.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="yes"/>
                <caption>Installing the Right Exhaust Manifold</caption>
                <calloutgroup>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Exhaust Manifold</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Mounting Stud Bolt (1)</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Mounting Bolt (7)</callout1>
                </calloutgroup>
            </figure>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Apply Never-Seez&#174; to the threads of the bolts.</para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Install right exhaust manifold (with gasket if required). Secure with seven mounting
                    bolts and one stud bolt. Tighten bolts in the specified sequence to the special torque value.
                </para>
            </step1>
            <figure id="f2050310a" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic filename="../figeg3/EG3307.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="no"/>
                <caption>Installing the Oil Level Gauge</caption>
                <calloutgroup>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Oil Level Gauge</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Nut</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Right Exhaust Manifold</callout1>
                </calloutgroup>
            </figure>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Install oil level gauge. Secure oil level gauge bracket to stud bolt with nut.</para>
            </step1>
            <figure id="f1200315" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic filename="../figeg3/EG3300.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="yes"/>
                <caption>Installing the EBP Sensor Tube</caption>
                <calloutgroup>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">EBP Sensor Tube</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">EBP Sensor Tube Nut</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Exhaust Manifold</callout1>
                </calloutgroup>
            </figure>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">If equipped, install EBP sensor tube to exhaust manifold and tighten nut.</para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Connect exhaust manifold to turbocharger exhaust tube. Tighten bolts to the special
                    torque value.
                </para>
            </step1>
        </svcproc>
    </svcsubsec>
